{{unreferenced|date=April 2012}} {{Infobox writer <!--For more information, see [[:Template:Infobox Writer/doc]].--> | name = Krushnaji Pandurang Kulkarni | honorific_prefix = | honorific_suffix = | image = | image_size = | alt = | caption = | native_name = कृष्णाजी पांडुरंग कुलकर्णी | native_name_lang = Devanagari | pseudonym = | birth_name = | birth_date = 1893 | birth_place = Maharashtra | death_date = 1964 | death_place = | resting_place = | occupation = | language = | nationality = Indian | citizenship = | education = | alma_mater = | period = | genre = <!-- or: | genres = --> | subject = <!-- or: | subjects = --> | movement = | notableworks = Marathi Bhasha Udgam Va Vikas, Marathi Vyutpatti Kosh, Rajwade Marathi Dhatu Kosh | spouse = <!-- or: | spouses = --> | partner = <!-- or: | partners = --> | children = | relatives = | awards = | signature = | signature_alt = | years_active = | module = | website = | portaldisp = <!-- "on", "yes", "true", etc; or omit --> }}
'''Krushnaji Pandurang Kulkani''' ([[Devanagari]]: कृष्णाजी पांडुरंग कुलकर्णी) (1893–1964) was a [[Marathi people|Marathi]] writer from [[Maharashtra]], [[India]].
In 1952, he presided over [[Marathi Sahitya Sammelan]], which was held in [[Amalner]].
The following is a partial list of Kulkarni's works: * Marathi Bhasha Udgam Va Vikas (मराठी भाषा उद्गम व विकास) * Marathi Vyutpatti Kosh (मराठी व्युत्पत्तिकोश) * Rajwade Marathi Dhatu Kosh (राजवाडे मराठी धातुकोश) (Editor) * Maharashtra Gatha (महाराष्ट्र गाथा) (Co-editor: [[Prahlad Keshav Atre]])
